    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1024990/extras/98054de0d40a9e3de065e1053d41f560.poster.avif?t=1553222121\" width=548 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1024990/extras/98054de0d40a9e3de065e1053d41f560.webm?t=1553222121\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1024990/extras/98054de0d40a9e3de065e1053d41f560.mp4?t=1553222121\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>WORDER</strong>是一个PC横向解谜游戏，角色会因应玩家在键盘上按下的的英文字母而改变自己的形状。玩家需要好好利用不同英文字母的特性和形状，解开各式各样的谜题，通过重重障碍。例如把物件运送到目的地或传动齿轮来开门。 WORDER充满各种可能性，谜题的解法亦不止一个答案， 让每个玩家在旅程中都有不一样的经历。<br><br>在游戏故事中，WORDER的母星正面对能源短缺，WORDERs 正在踏上一个在各个不同星球寻找能量的旅程。在旅程中，WORDER要好好运用自己的特点，变形成不同的英文字母去解决在面前出现的难题， 在各个星球寻找逗号能源， 带回母星。<br><br><strong><i>你的新旅程即将开始！ </i></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1024990/extras/76a3700cde7ec8f1d8cb95b8f58fed1e.webp?t=1553222121\" width=517 height=50 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1024990/extras/774597cffd93f1056592ada48b4665bb.webp?t=1553222121\" width=25 height=25 /></span> <strong>破解谜题</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1024990/extras/774597cffd93f1056592ada48b4665bb.webp?t=1553222121\" width=25 height=25 /></span> <strong>找出合适的字母</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1024990/extras/774597cffd93f1056592ada48b4665bb.webp?t=1553222121\" width=25 height=25 /></span> <strong>收集能量</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\"